  "description": "TCCC is not only a set of clinical tactics; it is an institutional process. Guidelines evolve through review of operational experience, clinical evidence, and feasibility under real constraints.\n¶Governance TCCC guidance is maintained and updated through formal committees and trauma systems within military medicine. Because the details change over time, treat any static summary as provisional and consult the current published guidance and your local protocol.\n",
